1
00:00:07,667 --> 00:00:08,917
- EARTH.

2
00:00:08,959 --> 00:00:10,750
FIRE.

3
00:00:10,792 --> 00:00:12,583
AIR.

4
00:00:12,625 --> 00:00:14,500
WATER.

5
00:00:14,542 --> 00:00:18,917
ONLY THE AVATAR CAN MASTER
ALL FOUR ELEMENTS

6
00:00:18,959 --> 00:00:20,917
AND BRING BALANCE
TO THE WORLD.

7
00:00:23,583 --> 00:00:25,041
[flute music]

8
00:00:27,250 --> 00:00:28,625
- BOLIN'S A HERO.

9
00:00:28,667 --> 00:00:30,834
THE MOVER STAR STOPPED
VARRICK'S KIDNAPPING ATTEMPT

10
00:00:30,875 --> 00:00:32,917
ON PRESIDENT RAIKO,
PROVING HIS BROTHER'S INNOCENCE.

11
00:00:32,959 --> 00:00:34,917
MAKO AND KORRA
WERE REUNITED,

12
00:00:34,959 --> 00:00:37,875
BUT KORRA HAS NO MEMORY
OF THEIR BREAKUP.

13
00:00:37,917 --> 00:00:39,709
MEANWHILE, JINORA'S SPIRIT
IS STILL TRAPPED

14
00:00:39,750 --> 00:00:40,792
IN THE SPIRIT WORLD,

15
00:00:40,834 --> 00:00:41,709
AND TONRAQ
AND HIS SOUTHERN FORCES

16
00:00:41,750 --> 00:00:42,792
HAVE BEEN DEFEATED.

17
00:00:42,834 --> 00:00:44,333
NOW IT'S UP TO TEAM AVATAR

18
00:00:44,375 --> 00:00:47,000
TO STOP UNALAQ
BEFORE HARMONIC CONVERGENCE.

19
00:00:47,667 --> 00:00:50,625
[flute music]

20
00:00:50,667 --> 00:00:58,291
♪ ♪

21
00:01:10,041 --> 00:01:12,959
- [grunting]

22
00:01:27,375 --> 00:01:29,375
- WHAT'S UP WITH THE COAT?

23
00:01:29,417 --> 00:01:31,083
AND WHERE DID YOU GET
THAT PIE?

24
00:01:31,125 --> 00:01:32,750
- IT'S A VARRICK SHIP.

25
00:01:32,792 --> 00:01:34,750
YOU NEVER KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE GONNA FIND.

26
00:01:34,792 --> 00:01:36,667
THERE'S A WHOLE LEVEL
FILLED WITH FUNHOUSE MIRRORS.

27
00:01:36,709 --> 00:01:39,750
OF COURSE,
THERE'S ALSO THE CAT-GATOR DECK.

28
00:01:39,792 --> 00:01:41,291
[sighs]

29
00:01:41,333 --> 00:01:42,834
I MISS THAT GUY.

30
00:01:42,875 --> 00:01:45,750
HE REALLY KNEW HOW TO MAKE
A LONG TRIP INTERESTING.

31
00:01:45,792 --> 00:01:47,834
SO HAVE YOU TOLD KORRA YET

32
00:01:47,875 --> 00:01:49,291
ABOUT HOW YOU GUYS BROKE UP
AND THEN YOU

33
00:01:49,333 --> 00:01:50,917
KIND OF STARTED DATING ASAMI
WHILE SHE WAS OFF

34
00:01:50,959 --> 00:01:52,625
GETTING ATTACKED
BY DARK SPIRITS?

35
00:01:52,667 --> 00:01:53,917
- YOU WANNA KEEP IT DOWN?

36
00:01:53,959 --> 00:01:56,000
I'M WAITING
FOR THE RIGHT MOMENT.

37
00:01:56,041 --> 00:01:58,041
- OH, MAKO.

38
00:01:58,083 --> 00:02:00,500
YOU KNOW, A WISE MAN ONCE
TOLD ME THAT DELIVERING BAD NEWS

39
00:02:00,542 --> 00:02:02,959
TO A GIRLFRIEND WAS LIKE RIPPING
OFF A BLOOD-SUCKING LEECH.

40
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:05,667
YOU JUST HAVE TO DO IT FAST
AND GET IT OVER WITH.

41
00:02:05,709 --> 00:02:08,375
- [groans]
I HATE IT WHEN YOU LISTEN TO ME.

42
00:02:08,417 --> 00:02:09,917
FINE.

43
00:02:09,959 --> 00:02:11,709
- UNALAQ WILL BE WAITING
FOR YOU.

44
00:02:11,750 --> 00:02:14,250
YOU'LL NEED ALL OF
YOUR AVATAR POWER TO STOP HIM.

45
00:02:14,291 --> 00:02:16,166
- I'M GOING TO CLOSE
THE SPIRIT PORTALS,

46
00:02:16,208 --> 00:02:19,000
LOCK VAATU IN
FOR ANOTHER 10,000 YEARS,

47
00:02:19,041 --> 00:02:22,291
AND MAKE UNALAQ WISH
HE'D NEVER BEEN BORN!

48
00:02:34,709 --> 00:02:35,792
THANKS, MAKO.

49
00:02:35,834 --> 00:02:38,917
- UH...UM...

50
00:02:38,959 --> 00:02:40,125
- DID YOU WANT SOMETHING?

51
00:02:40,166 --> 00:02:43,667
- UH, NO, NO, NOTHING.

52
00:02:43,709 --> 00:02:45,625
[groans]

53
00:02:48,375 --> 00:02:51,208
- AS SOON AS WE REACH
THE SOUTHERN WATER TRIBE,

54
00:02:51,250 --> 00:02:53,875
WE'LL BLAST THROUGH THE BLOCKADE
AT THE MAIN PORT.

55
00:02:53,917 --> 00:02:56,542
THEN WE CAN RENDEZVOUS
WITH TONRAQ AND HIS TROOPS,

56
00:02:56,583 --> 00:02:58,375
CRASH THROUGH THE DEFENSES
AROUND THE PORTAL,

57
00:02:58,417 --> 00:03:00,625
AND ENTER THE SPIRIT WORLD.

58
00:03:00,667 --> 00:03:02,875
- WHOA, SINCE WHEN
DOES MY LITTLE BROTHER

59
00:03:02,917 --> 00:03:05,125
WANT TO CRASH OR BLAST
THROUGH ANYTHING?

60
00:03:05,166 --> 00:03:08,083
- I'LL DO WHATEVER IT TAKES
TO SAVE MY DAUGHTER.

61
00:03:08,125 --> 00:03:10,041
- WE ALL WANT
TO SAVE JINORA,

62
00:03:10,083 --> 00:03:13,041
BUT I THINK YOUR PLAN
MIGHT BE A TAD OVERAGGRESSIVE,

63
00:03:13,083 --> 00:03:15,959
SEEING AS THERE ARE
ONLY SEVEN OF US AND ONE SHIP.

64
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:18,125
- REALLY?
AND WHAT DO YOU SUGGEST?

65
00:03:18,166 --> 00:03:21,458
- AN ATTACK LIKE THIS
CALLS FOR STRATEGY.

66
00:03:21,500 --> 00:03:23,875
I REMEMBER WHEN I WAS SURROUNDED
BY PIRATES

67
00:03:23,917 --> 00:03:25,709
IN THE HURRICANE STRAITS.

68
00:03:25,750 --> 00:03:27,709
WE MANAGED
TO CAPTURE THEM ALL

69
00:03:27,750 --> 00:03:31,000
WITH JUST A FEATHER, TWO EGGS,
AND A BARREL OF MOLASSES.

70
00:03:31,041 --> 00:03:32,959
- I DON'T WANT TO HEAR
ANY OF YOUR CRAZY STORIES NOW.

71
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:36,709
THIS IS SERIOUS.

72
00:03:36,750 --> 00:03:40,166
- ARE WE ALMOST THERE?
- ALMOST.

73
00:03:40,208 --> 00:03:43,041
BUT I JUST PICKED UP
A DISTRESS SIGNAL

74
00:03:43,083 --> 00:03:44,166
FROM THE SOUTHERN TROOPS.

75
00:03:44,208 --> 00:03:45,500
THERE'S A PROBLEM.

76
00:03:59,834 --> 00:04:01,375
- MOM!

77
00:04:03,250 --> 00:04:05,333
- I'M SO HAPPY YOU'RE HERE.

78
00:04:05,375 --> 00:04:07,917
- WHERE'S DAD?

79
00:04:07,959 --> 00:04:10,500
- UNALAQ WIPED OUT
THE ENTIRE SOUTHERN RESISTANCE

80
00:04:10,542 --> 00:04:13,125
AND CAPTURED YOUR FATHER.

81
00:04:13,166 --> 00:04:15,333
- I'LL GET HIM BACK.

82
00:04:15,375 --> 00:04:16,333
- WHERE IS MY MOTHER?

83
00:04:16,375 --> 00:04:18,500
- SHE'S IN THE HEALING HUT.

84
00:04:18,542 --> 00:04:20,792
SO MANY INJURED.

85
00:04:32,709 --> 00:04:34,250
- WHAT HAPPENED?

86
00:04:34,291 --> 00:04:36,917
- HER SOUL IS TRAPPED
IN THE SPIRIT WORLD.

87
00:04:36,959 --> 00:04:40,000
- OH, MY GOODNESS.
HOW LONG HAS SHE BEEN AWAY?

88
00:04:40,041 --> 00:04:41,834
- ALMOST A WEEK.

89
00:04:41,875 --> 00:04:43,583
I'VE TRIED TO KEEP
HER ENERGY FLOWING,

90
00:04:43,625 --> 00:04:45,750
BUT I CAN FEEL HER
SLIPPING AWAY.

91
00:04:45,792 --> 00:04:49,417
YOU'RE THE ONLY ONE
WHO CAN HELP HER NOW, MOM.

92
00:04:57,625 --> 00:04:59,250
- HOW MUCH LONGER
CAN SHE SURVIVE LIKE THIS?

93
00:04:59,291 --> 00:05:01,500
- I DON'T KNOW.

94
00:05:01,542 --> 00:05:05,750
BUT SHE'S VERY STRONG
TO HAVE LASTED THIS LONG.

95
00:05:07,417 --> 00:05:09,041
- I TALKED TO THE REBELS.

96
00:05:09,083 --> 00:05:10,917
THEY SAID UNALAQ'S GOT
THE SOUTHERN PORTAL SURROUNDED.

97
00:05:10,959 --> 00:05:13,500
HARMONIC CONVERGENCE
IS ONLY A FEW HOURS AWAY.

98
00:05:13,542 --> 00:05:15,750
- THEN WE HAVE TO BREAK THROUGH
THE ENEMY LINES OURSELVES

99
00:05:15,792 --> 00:05:17,333
AND GET TO THE PORTAL NOW.

100
00:05:17,375 --> 00:05:19,125
- THERE'S NO USE
IN TALKING ANYMORE.

101
00:05:19,166 --> 00:05:20,583
WE KNOW WHAT OUR MISSION IS.

102
00:05:20,625 --> 00:05:22,959
- A SUICIDE MISSION.

103
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:26,792
- YOU KNOW, I WAS
IN A SIMILAR SITUATION ONCE.

104
00:05:26,834 --> 00:05:28,583
MY PLATOON HAD CRAWLED
THROUGH THE DESERT

105
00:05:28,625 --> 00:05:30,291
WITH NO WATER FOR A WEEK,

106
00:05:30,333 --> 00:05:34,458
BUT WHEN WE FINALLY LOCATED
THE ONLY OASIS FOR 100 MILES,

107
00:05:34,500 --> 00:05:37,667
IT WAS SURROUNDED
BY ANGRY SANDBENDERS.

108
00:05:37,709 --> 00:05:40,250
I REALIZED OUR ONLY CHANCE
TO GET TO THE WATER

109
00:05:40,291 --> 00:05:43,000
WAS TO DROP IN FROM ABOVE.

110
00:05:43,041 --> 00:05:44,959
SO I FASHIONED TOGETHER
A CATAPULT,

111
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:47,458
AND WITH THE HELP OF
A FEW WELL-TRAINED HOG-MONKEYS--

112
00:05:47,500 --> 00:05:49,917
- ENOUGH
OF YOUR RIDICULOUS LIES.

113
00:05:49,959 --> 00:05:51,750
CAN'T YOU SEE
THAT THE FATE OF THE WORLD

114
00:05:51,792 --> 00:05:54,542
AND JINORA'S LIFE DEPENDS
ON WHAT WE DO HERE TODAY?

115
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:57,500
- HOLD ON.
MAYBE BUMI'S RIGHT.

116
00:05:57,542 --> 00:05:59,959
WE DON'T HAVE A CATAPULT
AND HOG-MONKEYS,

117
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:01,500
BUT WE HAVE A FLYING BISON,

118
00:06:01,542 --> 00:06:03,333
AND THERE'S A PLANE
ON VARRICK'S SHIP.

119
00:06:03,375 --> 00:06:05,291
MAYBE WE CAN ATTACK
FROM ABOVE.

120
00:06:05,333 --> 00:06:06,583
- WHAT ARE YOU THINKING?

121
00:06:06,625 --> 00:06:08,291
- MAKO, BOLIN, AND I
CAN USE THE PLANE

122
00:06:08,333 --> 00:06:09,750
TO CREATE A DISTRACTION

123
00:06:09,792 --> 00:06:11,500
AND SCATTER
SOME OF THE DEFENSES.

124
00:06:11,542 --> 00:06:13,500
YOU, TENZIN, BUMI,
AND KYA CAN FLY

125
00:06:13,542 --> 00:06:17,417
INTO THE SPIRIT PORTAL ON OOGI
WHEN YOU SEE AN OPENING.

126
00:06:17,458 --> 00:06:19,375
- LET'S GET MOVING.

127
00:06:24,125 --> 00:06:27,250
[animals whimper]

128
00:06:37,667 --> 00:06:39,792
- WHAT ARE WE STILL DOING HERE,
FATHER?

129
00:06:39,834 --> 00:06:43,041
- THE INVASION
WAS COMPLETELY SUCCESSFUL,

130
00:06:43,083 --> 00:06:45,500
AND THE SOUTHERN TRIBE
IS UNDER OUR CONTROL.

131
00:06:45,542 --> 00:06:47,291
THE SPIRIT PORTALS ARE OPEN.

132
00:06:47,333 --> 00:06:50,125
- YOU'VE RESTORED BALANCE.
NOW WE WOULD LIKE TO GO HOME.

133
00:06:50,166 --> 00:06:52,917
- YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND.

134
00:06:52,959 --> 00:06:56,083
EVERYTHING I'VE ACHIEVED SO FAR
WILL PALE IN COMPARISON

135
00:06:56,125 --> 00:06:57,792
WITH WHAT
I'M ABOUT TO ACCOMPLISH.

136
00:06:57,834 --> 00:07:01,083
- WHAT ELSE IS THERE?
THE WATER TRIBE IS UNITED.

137
00:07:01,125 --> 00:07:03,625
- AFTER TODAY, THERE WILL BE
NO MORE WATER TRIBE,

138
00:07:03,667 --> 00:07:05,750
NO MORE NATIONS OF ANY KIND.

139
00:07:05,792 --> 00:07:08,208
THE WORLD
IS ABOUT TO BE TRANSFORMED

140
00:07:08,250 --> 00:07:11,041
INTO SOMETHING MAGNIFICENT
AND NEW,

141
00:07:11,083 --> 00:07:15,625
AND I WILL LEAD
THIS GLORIOUS REVOLUTION.

142
00:07:15,667 --> 00:07:17,333
NOW GO OUTSIDE
AND GET THE TROOPS READY

143
00:07:17,375 --> 00:07:19,083
TO DEFEND THE SPIRIT PORTAL.

144
00:07:19,125 --> 00:07:22,250
- FROM WHOM?
WE'VE ALREADY BEATEN EVERYONE.

145
00:07:22,291 --> 00:07:24,333
- THE AVATAR
WILL BE HERE SOON.

146
00:07:24,375 --> 00:07:26,291
SHE HAS NO CHOICE.

147
00:07:40,959 --> 00:07:42,500
- ARE YOU READY?

148
00:07:42,542 --> 00:07:44,834
- I'M AN EARTHBENDER
STRAPPED TO THE WING OF A PLANE

149
00:07:44,875 --> 00:07:48,625
HUNDREDS OF FEET IN THE AIR,
SO NO.

150
00:07:48,667 --> 00:07:51,667
- DON'T WORRY. THERE'S NO WAY
THEY'LL BE EXPECTING THIS.

151
00:08:00,750 --> 00:08:03,291
- I THINK
THEY WERE EXPECTING IT.

152
00:08:28,417 --> 00:08:32,458
- [screams]
ASAMI!

153
00:08:34,125 --> 00:08:35,500
- GET READY.

154
00:08:44,125 --> 00:08:46,834
FIRE!

155
00:09:15,125 --> 00:09:17,083
- THERE ARE SPIRITS
EVERYWHERE.

156
00:09:17,125 --> 00:09:18,709
I DON'T SEE AN OPENING.

157
00:09:18,750 --> 00:09:21,041
- LET'S CIRCLE AROUND
AND SEE IF WE CAN FIND A WAY IN

158
00:09:21,083 --> 00:09:23,250
FROM THE OTHER SIDE.

159
00:09:25,291 --> 00:09:27,125
HOLD ON!

160
00:09:41,917 --> 00:09:43,875
[Oogi roars]

161
00:09:43,917 --> 00:09:45,542
THE SPIRITS ARE WEIGHING
OOGI DOWN.

162
00:09:45,583 --> 00:09:47,667
WE'RE LOSING ALTITUDE.

163
00:09:47,709 --> 00:09:51,667
- GET OFF OF HIM, YOU STICKY,
NASTY, LITTLE BLOB OF GOO!

164
00:09:51,709 --> 00:09:52,792
WHOA!

165
00:09:52,834 --> 00:09:55,375
IF I GO,
YOU'RE COMING WITH ME.

166
00:09:55,417 --> 00:09:58,333
AAH!

167
00:09:58,375 --> 00:10:00,083
- BUMI!

168
00:10:33,834 --> 00:10:36,750
- I WISH VARRICK
WAS FILMING THIS.

169
00:10:36,792 --> 00:10:40,083
WE COULD CALL IT
<i>NUKTUK: SKY WARRIOR.</i>

170
00:10:55,959 --> 00:10:57,458
- BRACE YOURSELVES.

171
00:11:08,709 --> 00:11:11,667
[Oogi grunts]

172
00:11:11,709 --> 00:11:14,834
[all grunt]

173
00:11:18,083 --> 00:11:21,709
- [groans]

174
00:11:35,125 --> 00:11:37,458
DAD.

175
00:11:39,709 --> 00:11:42,625
- KORRA,
I'M SO SORRY.

176
00:11:42,667 --> 00:11:44,417
I FAILED YOU.

177
00:11:44,458 --> 00:11:46,875
- DON'T GIVE UP.

178
00:11:46,917 --> 00:11:48,667
HARMONIC CONVERGENCE
ISN'T HERE YET.

179
00:11:48,709 --> 00:11:51,000
WE STILL HAVE A CHANCE.

180
00:11:51,041 --> 00:11:52,250
[whoosh]

181
00:11:52,291 --> 00:11:54,875
[all grunting]

182
00:11:57,542 --> 00:11:59,792
- WE TRIED.

183
00:11:59,834 --> 00:12:03,000
- CONGRATULATIONS, EVERYONE.

184
00:12:03,041 --> 00:12:05,166
YOU'VE ALL GOT
FRONT-ROW SEATS

185
00:12:05,208 --> 00:12:07,166
FOR THE BEGINNING
OF THE NEW WORLD ORDER.

186
00:12:07,208 --> 00:12:09,959
- YOU DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE DOING, UNALAQ.

187
00:12:10,041 --> 00:12:12,166
FREEING VAATU
WON'T MAKE YOU POWERFUL.

188
00:12:12,208 --> 00:12:14,166
IT WILL ONLY MAKE YOU A TRAITOR
TO EVERYTHING GOOD

189
00:12:14,208 --> 00:12:16,834
THAT'S HAPPENED
FOR THE LAST 10,000 YEARS.

190
00:12:16,875 --> 00:12:19,792
- YOU THINK WHAT AVATAR WAN
DID WAS GOOD?

191
00:12:19,834 --> 00:12:22,875
DRIVING ALMOST ALL THE SPIRITS
FROM THIS WORLD?

192
00:12:22,917 --> 00:12:26,750
THE AVATAR HASN'T BROUGHT
BALANCE, ONLY CHAOS.

193
00:12:26,792 --> 00:12:29,000
YOU CALL YOURSELF THE BRIDGE
BETWEEN THE TWO WORLDS,

194
00:12:29,041 --> 00:12:31,208
BUT THERE SHOULDN'T BE
A BRIDGE.

195
00:12:31,250 --> 00:12:33,291
WE SHOULD LIVE TOGETHER
AS ONE.

196
00:12:33,333 --> 00:12:34,834
- EVEN IF VAATU ESCAPES,

197
00:12:34,875 --> 00:12:37,375
I'LL PUT HIM RIGHT BACK
IN HIS PRISON,

198
00:12:37,417 --> 00:12:39,041
JUST LIKE WAN DID.

199
00:12:39,083 --> 00:12:41,000
- IT'S TRUE THAT,
WHEN WAN FUSED WITH RAAVA,

200
00:12:41,041 --> 00:12:43,625
HE TIPPED THE SCALES
IN HER FAVOR.

201
00:12:43,667 --> 00:12:46,458
BUT THIS TIME, I'LL BE HERE
TO LEVEL THE PLAYING FIELD.

202
00:12:46,500 --> 00:12:48,959
WHEN HARMONIC CONVERGENCE COMES,

203
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:51,625
I WILL FUSE WITH VAATU.

204
00:12:51,667 --> 00:12:53,750
AND TOGETHER, WE WILL BECOME
THE NEW AVATAR.

205
00:12:53,792 --> 00:12:57,417
A DARK AVATAR.

206
00:12:57,458 --> 00:12:59,542
YOUR ERA IS OVER.

207
00:12:59,583 --> 00:13:02,291
- THINK ABOUT WHAT
YOU'RE DOING.

208
00:13:02,333 --> 00:13:05,250
I KNOW THAT YOU'VE ALWAYS HAD
A DEEP CONNECTION

209
00:13:05,291 --> 00:13:09,458
WITH THE SPIRITS,
BUT YOU'RE STILL A MAN.

210
00:13:09,500 --> 00:13:11,166
YOU'RE STILL MY BROTHER.

211
00:13:11,208 --> 00:13:13,417
YOU'RE ESKA
AND DESNA'S FATHER.

212
00:13:13,458 --> 00:13:15,458
ARE YOU WILLING
TO THROW YOUR HUMANITY AWAY

213
00:13:15,500 --> 00:13:17,834
TO BECOME A MONSTER?

214
00:13:17,875 --> 00:13:21,166
- I'LL BE NO MORE OF A MONSTER
THAN YOUR OWN DAUGHTER.

215
00:13:21,208 --> 00:13:22,709
THE ONLY DIFFERENCE IS THAT,

216
00:13:22,750 --> 00:13:25,834
WHILE SHE CAN BARELY RECOGNIZE
HER OWN SPIRITUAL POWER,

217
00:13:25,875 --> 00:13:27,959
I WILL BE IN COMPLETE ALIGNMENT
WITH MINE.

218
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:30,166
VAATU AND I
WILL BE AS ONE.

219
00:13:30,208 --> 00:13:35,000
NO ONE WILL BE ABLE
TO STAND AGAINST US.

220
00:13:35,041 --> 00:13:36,500
KEEP THEM LOCKED UP.

221
00:13:36,542 --> 00:13:38,583
AFTER THE HARMONIC CONVERGENCE,

222
00:13:38,625 --> 00:13:41,333
I WILL COME FOR KORRA.

223
00:13:41,375 --> 00:13:42,667
- YES, FATHER.

224
00:13:46,542 --> 00:13:49,709
- I FAILED IN EVERY WAY.

225
00:13:49,750 --> 00:13:51,542
WE'VE LOST JINORA FOREVER.

226
00:13:51,583 --> 00:13:54,917
- THERE'S STILL A CHANCE.
THEY DIDN'T GET BUMI.

227
00:13:54,959 --> 00:13:56,000
- [groans]

228
00:14:02,500 --> 00:14:04,375
- [grunts]

229
00:14:04,417 --> 00:14:06,583
[spirit hissing]

230
00:14:06,625 --> 00:14:07,834
[screams]

231
00:14:12,959 --> 00:14:16,917
OH, YOU WANT
TO PLAY SOME MORE.

232
00:14:16,959 --> 00:14:19,583
WELL, BRING IT ON.

233
00:14:19,625 --> 00:14:23,792
[grunting]

234
00:14:32,709 --> 00:14:34,625
[chuckles]

235
00:14:44,500 --> 00:14:46,959
OH, WE'RE PLAYING DIRTY, HUH?

236
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:50,291
[grunts]

237
00:14:50,333 --> 00:14:53,750
[screams]

238
00:15:05,709 --> 00:15:08,667
[playing cheerful tune]

239
00:15:08,709 --> 00:15:12,583
♪ ♪

240
00:15:12,625 --> 00:15:16,333
HMM, LOOKS LIKE WE'VE GOT
A MUSIC LOVER HERE.

241
00:15:16,375 --> 00:15:24,458
♪ ♪

242
00:15:25,792 --> 00:15:28,417
[laughs]
REINFORCEMENTS!

243
00:15:31,709 --> 00:15:33,625
ALL RIGHT, SOLDIERS.

244
00:15:33,667 --> 00:15:36,458
LOOKS LIKE IT'S ON US
TO SAVE THE DAY.

245
00:15:36,500 --> 00:15:39,458
LUCKILY, I'VE GOT A PLAN.

246
00:15:46,875 --> 00:15:49,000
- ESKA, DESNA,
LISTEN TO ME.

247
00:15:49,041 --> 00:15:51,667
YOU'VE GOT TO HELP US
STOP UNALAQ.

248
00:15:51,709 --> 00:15:53,250
I KNOW HE'S YOUR FATHER,

249
00:15:53,291 --> 00:15:55,000
BUT VAATU HAS MADE HIM
COMPLETELY CRAZY.

250
00:15:55,041 --> 00:15:57,792
- WE WILL NEVER TURN
ON OUR FATHER.

251
00:15:57,834 --> 00:16:00,959
- PLEASE,
IF YOU LET ME OUT NOW,

252
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:03,709
I CAN STILL STOP HIM
FROM DESTROYING EVERYTHING.

253
00:16:03,750 --> 00:16:06,208
ONCE HE FUSES WITH VAATU,

254
00:16:06,250 --> 00:16:08,458
NO ONE WILL BE SAFE.

255
00:16:08,500 --> 00:16:11,917
DESNA, HE WON'T BE
YOUR FATHER ANYMORE.

256
00:16:14,625 --> 00:16:17,208
- YOU DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

257
00:16:17,250 --> 00:16:20,083
OUR FATHER IS THE WISEST MAN
IN THE WORLD.

258
00:16:20,125 --> 00:16:22,583
IF HE SAYS WHAT HE IS DOING
IS RIGHT,

259
00:16:22,625 --> 00:16:24,959
I BELIEVE HIM.

260
00:16:37,083 --> 00:16:40,458
- HUH?
[grunting]

261
00:16:40,500 --> 00:16:42,166
- YOU KNOW, IF I WANTED
SOME BALL OF EVIL

262
00:16:42,208 --> 00:16:43,583
LURKING OVER MY SHOULDER
ALL THE TIME,

263
00:16:43,625 --> 00:16:47,041
I'D HAVE STAYED HOME
WITH MY MOTHER-IN-LAW.

264
00:16:51,125 --> 00:16:52,458
- ALL RIGHT,
SPIRIT ARMY,

265
00:16:52,500 --> 00:16:54,792
YOUR GENERAL IS HERE.

266
00:16:54,834 --> 00:16:56,750
FOLLOW ME!

267
00:16:56,792 --> 00:17:03,625
♪ ♪

268
00:17:03,667 --> 00:17:06,750
IT'S WORKING.

269
00:17:06,792 --> 00:17:13,750
♪ ♪

270
00:17:13,792 --> 00:17:15,250
IT'S NOT WORKING.

271
00:17:19,542 --> 00:17:21,500
[panting]

272
00:17:21,542 --> 00:17:23,000
[gasps]

273
00:17:48,041 --> 00:17:50,125
GET ME OUT OF HERE!

274
00:18:11,917 --> 00:18:13,166
[shouts]

275
00:18:16,583 --> 00:18:19,917
[screams]

276
00:18:19,959 --> 00:18:22,458
WHOO-HOO!

277
00:18:22,500 --> 00:18:25,166
- AAH!

278
00:18:25,208 --> 00:18:29,959
- ALL RIGHT, GUYS.
RESCUE TIME.

279
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:32,125
[Eska and Desna shout]

280
00:18:38,792 --> 00:18:41,834
- BUMI, HOW DID YOU MANAGE TO
TAKE OUT THIS ENTIRE ENCAMPMENT

281
00:18:41,875 --> 00:18:43,500
ON YOUR OWN?

282
00:18:43,542 --> 00:18:46,458
- I DID IT ALL
WITH MY TRUSTY FLUTE AND--

283
00:18:46,500 --> 00:18:48,792
OH, NEVER MIND.
YOU WOULDN'T BELIEVE IT ANYWAY.

284
00:18:48,834 --> 00:18:50,417
LET'S GET MOVING.

285
00:19:03,917 --> 00:19:06,625
- YOU RUN INTO THE PORTAL.

286
00:19:06,667 --> 00:19:08,959
I'LL TRY TO HOLD OFF ANYONE
WHO COMES AFTER YOU.

287
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:11,542
- NO, YOU'RE TOO HURT.
YOU NEED A HEALER.

288
00:19:11,583 --> 00:19:15,250
ASAMI, CAN YOU TAKE OOGI
AND MY DAD BACK TO MY MOM?

289
00:19:15,291 --> 00:19:17,917
- MM-HMM.
- THIS IS MY FIGHT NOW.

290
00:19:17,959 --> 00:19:20,417
- KORRA.

291
00:19:20,458 --> 00:19:21,917
I LOVE YOU.

292
00:19:21,959 --> 00:19:24,625
- I LOVE YOU TOO, DAD.

293
00:19:24,667 --> 00:19:28,041
- YIP-YIP.

294
00:19:34,792 --> 00:19:36,917
- ONCE WE'RE INSIDE,
YOU GO FIND JINORA.

295
00:19:36,959 --> 00:19:39,375
MAKO AND BOLIN
WILL TAKE CARE OF UNALAQ

296
00:19:39,417 --> 00:19:41,500
WHILE I CLOSE THE PORTAL,
SO VAATU CAN'T ESCAPE.

297
00:19:41,542 --> 00:19:43,750
- WAIT A SECOND.
WORST-CASE SCENARIO.

298
00:19:43,792 --> 00:19:45,875
SO WE'RE FIGHTING UNALAQ,
YOU CLOSE THE PORTALS,

299
00:19:45,917 --> 00:19:49,250
AND LET'S JUST SAY
SOMETHING HAPPENS TO YOU.

300
00:19:49,291 --> 00:19:52,208
ARE WE GONNA BE TRAPPED
IN THERE FOR ETERNITY?

301
00:19:52,250 --> 00:19:54,542
- IF EVERYTHING
GOES AS PLANNED,

302
00:19:54,583 --> 00:19:57,375
WE'LL ALL WALK OUT TOGETHER
AFTER HARMONIC CONVERGENCE.

303
00:19:57,417 --> 00:19:58,709
IF NOT...

304
00:20:04,583 --> 00:20:06,250
[sighs]

305
00:20:06,291 --> 00:20:07,083
LET'S GO.

306
00:20:32,917 --> 00:20:36,125
TENZIN, GO FIND JINORA.

307
00:20:36,166 --> 00:20:38,125
- COME ON!

308
00:21:28,583 --> 00:21:31,458
- YOU'RE RUNNING OUT OF TIME,
RAAVA.

309
00:21:31,500 --> 00:21:34,083
I KNOW YOU FEEL IT COMING.

310
00:21:41,417 --> 00:21:43,208
- [grunts]

311
00:22:02,291 --> 00:22:05,208
[both grunt]

312
00:22:55,750 --> 00:23:01,500
- [laughing maniacally]
